    "name": "末日漫游指南",
    "steam_appid": 3321680,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>末日来临，丧尸病毒爆发....</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >屋漏偏逢连夜雨，你的女儿患有慢性哮喘，身为父亲的你首要任务就是去一趟医院，尽管那里现在充满危险....</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321680/extras/ad56aa0c96f3548dba51aaa49a215d9c.avif?t=1761541083\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*合理规划资源：食物、饮料、水，可烹饪食材...确保你和女儿的身体状况良好。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321680/extras/da28f31ae1746ec485b805e4bf69d1bf.avif?t=1761541083\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建造、升级你的藏身处，为自己的女儿，以及幸存者打造庇护所。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321680/extras/70a24c495a4c448aa5bc2fe446cedb5f.avif?t=1761541083\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >搜刮建筑物，发现幸存者，接纳为队友，对队友的态度会影响后续的游戏进程！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*拥有多种武器可供选择：近战武器、手枪、霰弹枪，突击步枪....并可在工程师处定制升级。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321680/extras/91c2adcfae3cb515022bdded94faac8c.avif?t=1761541083\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >和幸存者共同战斗，也可以让他在家里保护女儿，为你赢得更多探索时间。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321680/extras/6301314f611825c5ce135af8a3348997.avif?t=1761541083\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一本末日漫游指南，上面写了末日来临时你需要做的每一件事，猥琐发育，安全第一，保护女儿！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321680/extras/84c9056dac39349f9784ee5591a06258.avif?t=1761541083\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*面对源源不尽的尸潮，关卡设计会提供重型火力帮助抵抗</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321680/extras/933a50c44611fcdc4f82130112a98a00.avif?t=1761541083\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321680/extras_big/933a50c44611fcdc4f82130112a98a00.avif?t=1761541083 width=800 height=554 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321680/extras/ff1e7bff8fb333f745ed831600a9f994.avif?t=1761541083\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321680/extras_big/ff1e7bff8fb333f745ed831600a9f994.avif?t=1761541083 width=800 height=627 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*肆意搜索每一栋大楼！小心，大楼内部充满未知，需要帮助的NPC，不怀好意的敌人等......</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*大量文本剧情填充，以线性剧情为主，并提供了分支选项，您的每一个选择都会影响某个NPC，或者玩家自己的命运。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*交流群：733742575</p>",
